{"title":"气象娜美","authors":["华谋"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"气象娜美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔侗族〕华谋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八音芦笙好响亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震动了层层山岭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位能干的娜美①，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四团八寨传颂着她的名声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓楼的喇叭响了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又传来了娜美的声音："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今天下午有雷雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家注意庄稼别受损失。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一回、两回、三回……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说雨就雨、说晴就晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人眯起了眼睛："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席教侗家娜美做大事情。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她和伙伴们挤上鼓楼坪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗汉②们又爱慕又拘谨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娜美的百折裙先舞起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗汉才靦觍地唱歌邀请。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是她的发髻分外黑亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是她百折裙格外秀丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是侗家第一个气象娜美啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不深深地受人尊敬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注①娜美：少女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②罗汉：未婚男青年。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}